Dialogs.Dialog: Hey. How long are you gonna stay in bed？
That's good. Hey, if you don't get up, we'll be late.
Someone said that he could barely get up in the morning, right？ Now, get ready！
Did you forget？ I told you I'd help you get up.
Why don't you stay here？ I'll just get dressed and I'll be ready...
I'll be waiting outside. Just hurry up.
I promised you, right？ So now I'm here to wake you up. Hey, are you still half asleep？
Um, my brain hasn't woken up yet.
...Then shall I get in bed with you until you fully wake up？
Haha, now you're awake. Get ready, okay？
If you don't get up, I'll leave...
Wait... I wanna buy some potatoes first...
I'll wait outside. You'd better hurry, okay？
Just a little bit more... You should sleep too. Come on, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey... I'll give you a little more time. I'll wake you up in a bit, okay？
Hehe. Looking at you like this, I want to sleep on your bed too.
Hehe, no thanks. Wake up, okay？ We're gonna be late.
Hey, have you bought your lunch yet？
A lunch box？ You made it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Ah, sorry. I'm just so happy.
Then I won't blame you. Oh well... Is a Japanese styled lunch okay for you？
Um, well... I wonder if you already had lunch...
I'm about to go buy it...
Great. Here. I was hoping you would try this...
A lunch box？ Is it for me？
Yes. I made it myself. ...Please try it.
If you don't like it, please tell me.
Hey, have you bought your lunch？
Huh？ Ah, could it be a homemade lunch box？
Oh, awesome！ Wonderful. Thank you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
You're welcome. Please let me know how you like it. I'll surely try harder next time.
Very delicious. Your soup base and the seasonings are well blended...
Hey, how many times are you going to praise me？
It's just too delicious that I can't help praising you.
I see. You can't help it, eh？ Hehe！
Today's lunch is so tasty！ Your stew is the best ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey, what shall I cook for you next？
Your food is always so delicious. So anything's okay, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Really？ I'm so happy... Then I'll also try my best next time.
Perfect. Your flavor is the best, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hehe. Very well. I wonder what I should make next. You have any requests？
Hehe, yo！ I made a lunch box today.
Lunch box？ Then I'll go buy a sandwich and we can eat together.
Oh, a Western-styled lunch！ Looks yummy. Can I really eat it？
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Wait a sec. I'll go buy my lunch, so we can eat together...
Wait. I knew you would say that. That's why I hurried here.
Ah, do you have anything you want to eat in particular？
No, that's not the case. Here. I want you to try this.
Yes. It's Western food though. If it's okay, please have some.
Hehe. Seeing your happy face makes me happy too. Here you go.
Hehe. I'm going to kidnap you.
I don't have money though. What do you want？
What shall I request then...？ Here.
Yes. I want you to eat this. How's that？
Am I drooling or something...？ From the smell, this must be Western food.
Hehe, bingo. Hey, why don't you hurry and eat it？
Oh, delicious！ I'm looking forward to the next one.
You're very good at cheering people up, huh？
I'm really looking forward to it. It's like I've discovered something new for every bite I took...
Yeah. I added so many things that you wanted to eat in it. How is it？
Very delicious！ The last one was delicious but this one is perfect！ It's my favorite.
...I'm glad that I added more stuff in it.
It's very delicious. Wow, you really can cook delicious food.
You can still praise me even more？
Your food is so delicious. I want more, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Hehe. Roger that. You can look forward to it▼
...A lunch box？ Is that for me？
If you don't want it, I'll just eat it alone.
I want it！ Yes, I want it！
Hmm. It's Chinese food though. Is it good？
Of course！ So you can also can cook Chinese food. Hmm... It looks yummy, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Please try it and let me know what you think. Here you go.
Um, hey... Have you already bought your lunch？
No, I'm about to. Eh？ What's that you're carrying？
...Um, it's the lunch I made. Shall we eat together？
Oh, thank you！ What did you make？
Chinese food. Hey, you said earlier that you like it, right？
Oh, it looks luxurious. Thank you so much.
Okay. Let me know how you like it after you finish it, okay？
I really want to know your preferences.
Oh, great. Just wait a sec. I'll go buy my lunch.
You don't have to. I made some for you.
If you're not in the mood for Chinese food, you can buy your own...
Hehe. Just seeing your happy face makes me feel like it is really worth it to cook this.
Then shall we start eating？ I want to hear your opinion, so please savor it, okay？
Yes, it's Chinese food... How is it？
Delicious！ I feel like your food is spicing up my spirits.
Hehe. That's probably because I actually put spices in there.
Yeah, you can feel them, right？ Hehe. You'd better hurry and eat it.
Hehe, you're in such good mood... What do you think about the side dish today？
...Very delicious！ It's so delicious that I'm full of joy now.
Hearing you say that, I'm now so full of joy too. I'm kidding.
Yup, today's Chinese food is also delicious！
But, for you to cook such wonderful food, it must be quite troublesome. I love to eat it, but...
No problem. Seeing your smile when you eat it is the best reward for me.
...I'm kidding. Hey, what do you want to eat next time？
